Etihad Atheeb Shareholders Vote to Continue Operations

-- B y   M o u r a d   H a r o u t u n i a n
-- 
2011-04-17T06:48:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-17/etihad-atheeb-shareholders-vote-to-continue-operations.html
Etihad Atheeb Telecommunications
Co.’s shareholders voted to continue with the company’s
operations, it said a statement to the Saudi bourse today.  Saudi Arabia ’s Capital Market Authority had given Etihad
Atheeb a March 31 deadline to amend its financial position as
the company accumulated losses that exceeded 75 percent of its
capital.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mourad Haroutunian in Riyadh at 
